{"fields":[{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasPrompt"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealPrompt1"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealPrompt2"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealPrompt3"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealPrompt4"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealPrompt5"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealPrompt6"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealJoke0"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealJoke1"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealJoke2"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealJoke3"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealJoke4"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealJoke5"},{"t":"A","s":"Wo ist der schlimmste Ort, an dem man eine Schlange finden kann?","n":"RevealPrompt1"},{"t":"A","s":"Wie würdest du die Zeit in einem dunklen Raum ohne Kontakt zur Außenwelt verbringen?","n":"RevealPrompt2"},{"t":"A","s":"Welches unserer Haushaltsgeräte wird sich in Zukunft zuerst gegen die Menschheit wenden?","n":"RevealPrompt3"},{"t":"A","s":"Was verstecken Clowns in ihren übergroßen Schuhen?","n":"RevealPrompt4"},{"t":"A","s":"Was ist derzeit das sauberste Ding in diesem Raum?","n":"RevealPrompt5"},{"t":"A","s":"Was sind die größten Krisen, mit denen du in deinem Leben konfrontiert warst?","n":"RevealPrompt6"},{"t":"A","s":"Wie bewegen sich die Dinger überhaupt?!","v":"joke1","n":"RevealJoke0"},{"t":"A","s":"Klaus, Klaus, Klaus...","v":"joke2","n":"RevealJoke1"},{"t":"A","s":"","n":"RevealJoke2"},{"t":"A","s":"Wer <i>will</i> das denn beruflich machen?!?","v":"joke4","n":"RevealJoke3"},{"t":"A","s":"Wieso sieht man die nicht!?!","v":"joke5","n":"RevealJoke4"},{"t":"A","s":"Man selbst ist dabei so hilflos...","v":"joke6","n":"RevealJoke5"},{"t":"A","s":"Welche von diesen ist eure tiefste Angst?","v":"prompt","n":"Prompt"}]}